<html>
<head>
    <title>Email template</title>
</head>
<body style="margin : 0px; 
             padding : 0px;">
     
    <div style="
            margin : 50px auto;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif">
        <div style="
                 width: 450px;
                 background : white;
                 text-align : center;
                 border-radius : 4px;
                 padding : 20px 50px 40px;
                 margin: 0px auto;
                 background: #ffffff8a;
                 border: 1px solid #06b7f9;
                 ">
                <h1 style="
                        font-size: 46px;
                        font-weight: 700;
                        color: #02a2de;
                        padding: 0px;
                        margin: 0px;
                      "> Instapic </h1>
                <p style="
                    font-weight : 500;
                    font-size : 22px;
                    margin-bottom : 0px;
                    padding : 0px;
                   ">
                    Password Reset Request.
                </p>
                <p style="font-weight : 500;
                          font-size : 16px;
                          margin-top : 5px;
                          padding:  0px;
                          ">
                    It seems like you are trying to reset your password. If yes? Then please 
					click the link below to reset your password. 
                </p>
                <button style="
                        padding: 14px 25px 12px;
                        margin-top: 5px;
                        font-size: 16px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                        background-color: #125bffeb;
                        border: none;
                       ">
                    <a href="<%= link %>" style="text-decoration: none; color : white">Reset Password</a>
                </button>
                 <p style="
                    font-weight : 500;
                    font-size : 16px; 
                    margin-top : 35px;
                    text-align: center;
                    color : #1d1da2;
                    padding:  0px;"> 
                    If you are not requested this please ignore this email.<br>
					Thank you
                </p>
        </div>
        <div style="
            width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 5px 25px;
            margin: 15px auto;
            background: #fd989861;
              ">
            <p style="
              text-align : start;
              font-size : 14px;
              font-weight : 600;
              color : #e91e63;
              ">
              Note: Please do not post inappropriate images. Otherwise,
              The admin can take strict action on your account. In the
              worst-case scenario, your account may be blocked.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
      

</body>
</html>